REPAIR WALL COVERING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
To repair tears or loose edges in wall coverings, just hold the wall covering 
away from the wall surface. Then apply paste to the wall ans to the back of the 
wall covering before pressing it back into place, using a seam roller. Use a 
damp sponge to remove excess paste. 
</P>
