<HEADLINE>
<P>
ISRAEL DREAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Last year for the first time I went to Israel in March. 
</P>
<P>
I loved it so much that I returned with my family in November. Israel is a 
tourist's dream. Great food, lovely accommodations, history, modern cities and 
sites that leave you breathless. 
</P>
<P>
Some recommendations: Laromme Hotel in Jerusalem, lovely accommodations, indoor 
heated pool and a very helpful staff; La Pasta restaurant, Jerusalem. A tour 
guide is a must; my family and I spent four days with Gozal Ben Shaul who 
speaks excellent English and is well-versed historically. He can design a tour 
to fit interests. His number is (04) 336-779. 
</P>
<P>
JUDY MARTINEZ 
</P>
<P>
Topanga 
</P>
