<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAVORING SAFARI 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Having recently returned from a safari in Kenya, I thought you might want to 
know about the marvelous accommodations, great restaurants and amenities of the 
Safari Park on the outskirts of Nairobi. 
</P>
<P>
The rates were reasonable and the extensive park-like grounds were lush, green 
and extremely well kept. 
</P>
<P>
I heartily recommend the Safari Park Hotel, P.O. Box 45038, Nairobi, Kenya, as 
one of the best. 
</P>
<P>
THEODORE H. FINNEY 
</P>
<P>
Culver City 
</P>
