<DOCID> 161921 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 14, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 10; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
