<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski made a $21 profit when Vigorous Green won the 
sixth race and returned $3.20 to win. 
</P>
<P>
His $35 parlay turned into a straight win bet when his first horse, Burn Annie, 
was scratched in the fifth race. Bob, who started the meeting with a mythical 
$1,000 bankroll, is now at $1,136. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is $50 to win on Kamikaze Sam in the ninth. 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Bankroll $1,115 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Profit $21 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll $1,136 
</P>
