<P>
JACKSONVILLE, Fla. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A pilot for convicted drug kingpin Carlos Lehder Rivas has been sentenced to 
two consecutive life terms and fined $2 million by a federal judge. 
</P>
<P>
Jack Carlton Reed, 59, of Los Angeles, was sentenced Friday for his October 
