on a John Wayne Airport flight heading to San Francisco, where L.A. and the 
49ers face off today for the NFC championship. The hundreds of Rams supporters 
who made their way to San Francisco found no lack of football fever. And San 
Franciscans found no lack of Rams fans. AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
