<DATE>
<P>
January 14, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
DARYL F GATES 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
