he announced he would not run for mayor -- despite T-shirt at left, a gift from 
his staff. LARRY DAVIS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Bulldog Edition) There also 
were difficult moments, including the one above, in 1989, when he and Sheriff 
Sherman Block announced the arrest of a deputy in a multiple murder case. 
Charges were dropped when tests revealed the deputy's gun wasn't the murder 
weapon. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
